\begin_layout Standard
Conclusion:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This paper advocates a novel prior-free approach to nonrigid factorization.
 Our method is purely convex, very easy to implement, and is guaranteed
 to converge to an optimal solution 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(at least approximately up to certain relaxation).
\end_layout

